@startuml
title Evenite Event Registration Process

actor Student
participant "Frontend" as FE
participant "Event Service" as EventS
participant "Database" as DB
participant "Notification Service" as Notif

Student -> FE: Browse events
FE -> EventS: Request events
EventS -> DB: Fetch events
DB --> EventS: Return events
EventS --> FE: Display events
FE -> Student: Show events

Student -> FE: Select event
FE -> EventS: Check capacity
EventS -> DB: Get registration count
DB --> EventS: Return count
EventS --> FE: Confirm availability
FE -> Student: Show registration form

Student -> FE: Submit registration
FE -> EventS: Process registration
EventS -> DB: Save registration
DB --> EventS: Confirmation
EventS -> Notif: Send confirmation
Notif -> Student: Notification
EventS --> FE: Registration success
FE -> Student: Display confirmation
@enduml